Billing_Frequency_Begins_With_Vowel__c.calculatedFormula:
OR(
  AND(
    NOT( TEXT( Billing_Frequency__c ) = 'Custom' )
    ,CASE(
        UPPER( LEFT( TEXT( Billing_Frequency__c ), 1 ) ),
        'A', 1,
        'E', 1,
        'I', 1,
        'O', 1,
        'U', 1,
        0
    ) = 1
    
  )
,
AND(
    TEXT( Billing_Frequency__c ) = 'Custom' 
    ,CASE(
        UPPER( LEFT( Custom_Billing_Frequency__c , 1 ) ),
        'A', 1,
        'E', 1,
        'I', 1,
        'O', 1,
        'U', 1,
        0
    ) = 1
    
  )


)
Billing_Frequency_Begins_With_Vowel__c.label: Billing Frequency Begins With Vowel?
Billing_Frequency_Begins_With_Vowel__c.name: Billing_Frequency_Begins_With_Vowel__c
